headline: Costco’s Unusual Options Activity Provides Income Investors With Good Opportunity
summary: Costco's options volume wasn't particularly thrilling on Thursday. However, its unusual options activity consisted of two put options among the top 389 on the day. Both provide income investors with a good opportunity to profit.

headline: Costco Stock Rated Buy as UBS Highlights Growth Potential in Extended Hours Pilot
summary: Costco Wholesale Corporation (NASDAQ:COST) ranks among the best set-it-and-forget-it stocks to buy.
